rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0001
rows.name:
Why have we not received confirmation
that the target is destroyed? What is the delay?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0002
rows.name: Grandmaster, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0003
rows.name:
The target appears to have
some manner of customized trion barrier...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0004
rows.name: A TRION barrier?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0005
rows.name: Are you daft? These are HUMANS we're talking about.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0006
rows.name:
No one outside of the Qlu system
has access to Trion technology![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0007
rows.name:
And those Skells of theirs... How did a primitive race
like theirs manage to piece those together?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0008
rows.name:
As you say, Grandmaster.
But if they are truly the Founders' descendants...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0009
rows.name:
Don't speak to me of myths—hah!
A tale to frighten children![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0010
rows.name:
They are the disease, not the cure!
They are NOT the failsafe...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0011
rows.name: Number four cupola is down![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0012
rows.name: Heavy damage sustained in turret cluster three![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0013
rows.name: The enemy forces are rallying![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0014
rows.name: Sir, we can no longer effectively strike the target![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0015
rows.name: Where are the interceptors?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0016
rows.name: An enemy detachment has cut them off! They can't reach us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0017
rows.name:
But these are SAVAGES! Not...
No—I refuse to believe it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0018
rows.name: Prepare the Vita! I shall crush them myself![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0019
rows.name: Grandmaster—with all due respect, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0020
rows.name:
The Vita belongs to the Great One.
Your body could not withstand it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0021
rows.name: The Great One's blood runs in these veins![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs12070100_MSG0022
rows.name: I WILL use it...because I MUST use it.[ST:wait ]
